{
  "$comment": "Single source of truth for contract-artifact versioning. Maps a team's Officer-generation tag (TeamOfficer.version in the backend DB, e.g. 'legacy' / 'v0.10') to a coarse artifact-folder version ('v1' / 'v2'), and records which Ignition module keys back each contract type per version. All four consumers (app, dashboard, backend, ponder) receive a copy as 'version-registry.json' via `npm run mc`. Structure is kept as FLAT string maps (like deployed_addresses) so prettier formats it identically at any printWidth across every consumer. See contract/UPGRADE_STRATEGY.md and .claude/plans.",
